## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-104">低耦合提供者裝載的應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-104">Decoupled providers are hosted by an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-105">將 WMI 類別的執行個體提供應用程式可以使用兩種方法： 發佈/撤銷或回呼方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-105">Two methods can be used by the application to make instances of WMI classes available: publish/revoke or the callback method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-106">回呼方法會使用<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A>和<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-106">The callback method uses the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A> and <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-107">在發佈/revoke 模型中，WMI 基礎結構會提供預設行為，提供了許多您不必自行撰寫回呼方法中的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-107">In the publish/revoke model, the WMI infrastructure provides default behavior for many of the methods you have to write yourself in the callback method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-108">其中包含列舉型別，以及繫結方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-108">These include the enumeration and bind methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-109">在此模型中，應用程式會建立執行個體，並將其發行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-109">In this model, the application creates instances and publishes them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-110">應用程式會負責確保會遵守類別的索引鍵屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-110">The application is responsible for ensuring that the key properties of the classes are respected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-111">應用程式也會負責刪除執行個體的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-111">The application is also responsible for deleting instances.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-112">在回呼模型中，WMI 基礎結構會預期要有方法可處理列舉型別、 繫結和實作的提供者的功能所需的任何其他方法的應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-112">In the callback model, the WMI infrastructure expects the application to have methods that handle enumeration, binding and any other methods required to implement the functionality of the provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-113">它會呼叫這項功能的應用程式如果它不存在或未正確實作就會失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-113">It calls into the application for this functionality and fails if it does not exist or is not implemented properly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-114">應用程式與基礎結構註冊其 WMI 類別的型別，藉由呼叫<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A>，並指出它不再想要藉由呼叫公開的 WMI 類別<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-114">The application registers the type of its WMI classes with the infrastructure by calling <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A> and indicates that it no longer wants the WMI classes exposed by calling <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-115">下列範例示範如何使用發行/撤銷模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-115">The following example demonstrates how to use the publish/revoke model.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-116">建立並發佈兩個路由器類別執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-116">Two instances of the router class are created and published.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-117">稍後撤銷。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-117">They are later revoked.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class Sample_InstanceProvider  
{  
public int Main (string[] args)   
{  
Router r_one = new Router ();  
r_one.Name = "one";  
InstrumentationManager.Publish(r_one);  
Router r_two = new Router ();  
r_two.Name = "two";  
InstrumentationManager.Publish(r_two);  
// ....  
InstrumentationManager.Revoke(r_one);  
InstrumentationManager.Revoke(r_two);  
return 0;  
}  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="de4b1-118">在下一個範例中，註冊的回呼方法用來將 RouterNew 類別公開。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de4b1-118">In the next example, the callback method of registration is used to expose the RouterNew class.</span></span>  
  
```  
public int MainNew(string[] args)   
{  
    InstrumentationManager.RegisterType(typeof(RouterNew));  
    // ....  
    InstrumentationManager.UnRegisterType(typeof(RouterNew));  
    return 0;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```  
static int Main(string[] args)  
{  
   InstrumentationManager.RegisterType(typeof(MySampleProvider));  
   return 0;  
}  
